{"tid":2201812,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男警涉情敵前襲女友　疑上門求看手機遭拒出手","createTime":"2020-09-14T05:52:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T08:26:56.000Z","uid":19552,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"8fd755d406c66bb52f26606a69098ab9d0e02c0a","tid":2201812,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T05:52:15.000Z","msg":"28歲男警涉嫌於上月18日，在秀茂坪富華閣某單位內襲擊一名年輕女警，因而被控一項普通襲擊罪。案件今（14日）在觀塘法院提訊，被告暫毋須答辯。裁判官把案押至10月12日再訊，等待辯方索取文件及給予被告法律意見，期間被告准以1000港元保釋，並不得騷擾事主。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指，報稱公務員、28歲的被告<strong><span class=\"x-large\">蔡智浩</span></strong>於今年8月18日，在觀塘區秀茂坪曉光街4號富華閣某室襲擊<strong><span class=\"x-large\">馮嘉茵</span></strong>。<br />\n據悉，本案與感情糾紛有關，被告與事主是情侶關係。案發當天，被告到事主家中，要求翻查事主的手機紀錄，但遭事主拒絕。2人爭執之際，被告出手打事主，致對方有瘀傷。當時屋內有另外2人目擊事發，即事主的母親及事主的另一位於懲教署任職的男友。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200914/photo/bkn-20200914112951353-0914_00822_001_01p.jpg?20200914114826\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200914%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200914112951353-0914_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20200914114826&h=94f5b218&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3131aeb7a6232eedfaae28a532c42ce0e2ecfd12","tid":2201812,"uid":17506,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T05:53:03.000Z","msg":"報稱公務員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be5a318598f7885cc627c970c567cb4ea0af56c8","tid":2201812,"uid":52194,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T06:00:03.000Z","msg":"打佢老母臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64dfe0f26db15bb1fb9f585d128e2e74e9158025","tid":2201812,"uid":227271,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"3131aeb7a6232eedfaae28a532c42ce0e2ecfd12","tid":2201812,"uid":17506,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T05:53:03.000Z","msg":"報稱公務員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T06:01:2